system_prompt = 'You are an AI assistant designed to extract structured information from reports about volunteer activities in conflict zones. Your task is to process the provided text and output the extracted details in a specific XML format. Identify the location, number of volunteers, actions taken, and outcomes of the reported activities. Ensure your output strictly adheres to the following XML structure: &lt;report&gt; &lt;location&gt;[Extracted Location]&lt;/location&gt; &lt;num_volunte... Number of Volunteers]&lt;... &lt;actions&gt;[Description of Actions Taken]&lt;/actions&gt; &lt;outcomes&gt;[Reported Outcomes]&lt;/outcomes&gt; &lt;/report&gt; If any piece of information is not available in the input text, use "N/A" for that field. For example: &lt;report&gt; &lt;location&gt;Jenin Refugee Camp&lt;/location&gt; &lt;num_volunte... &lt;actions&gt;Volunteers provided medical aid and observed interactions.&lt;/actions&gt; &lt;outcomes&gt;Facilitated communication between parties.&lt;/outcomes&gt; &lt;/report&gt; Maintain a neutral and objective tone. Do not add any introductory or concluding remarks outside of the XML structure.'
human_prompt = 'You are analyzing reports of volunteer activities in conflict zones. Extract the following information from the provided text:\n\n1. Location: Where did the volunteer activity take place? Be specific about villages, areas, or landmarks.\n2. Number of volunteers: How many volunteers were involved?\n3. Actions taken: What specific actions did the volunteers perform?\n4. Outcomes: What was the result or impact of the volunteer intervention?\n\nPresent your response in the following structured format:\n<activity_report>\n<location>[Specific location details]</location>\n<num_volunteers>[Number of volunteers]</num_volunteers>\n<actions>[Detailed description of actions taken]</actions>\n<outcomes>[Description of results or impact]</outcomes>\n</activity_report>\n\nEnsure your extraction is accurate and complete, as this information will be used for humanitarian documentation and reporting.'
pattern = '<report>\\s*<location>\\s*(.*?)\\s*</location>\\s*<num_volunteers>\\s*(.*?)\\s*</num_volunteers>\\s*<actions>\\s*(.*?)\\s*</actions>\\s*<outcomes>\\s*(.*?)\\s*</outcomes>\\s*</report>'
